<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">
Slovakia, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Liptovskě">Liptovske</normalizedToken>
hole, Zuberec, Osobita, 1650-1680 m, 1935, Suza (PRM-765231!, syntype).
</paragraph>
